While the trailers for the Gal Gadot-led film have so far been met with praise, the latest “origin” trailer has caused outrage from some sectors of the internet. At around the 1.40 mark, the actor raises her arms, exposing her armpit. However, as noted by many, the pit looks remarkably smooth and has a strangely grey skin tone. It may have only been seconds, but numerous people have taken issue with what appears to be either weird fake tan or a photoshopped mess. Slate probed the scenario, questioning whether they were bleached in post-production and wondering why the creases were removed. The film’s villain was finally revealed, confirming comic-book stalwart Ares, the God of War will be Wonder Woman’s nemesis. The Independent